feat(ui): improve add-product flow and preserve expanded row state

- Add product (new mode): Now fetches data first from the URL automatically,
  shows a preview with Approve button. Manual brand/model override only revealed
  if user clicks 'Not right - edit manually', removing the need to pre-enter anything.
- Expanded product rows now stay open after adding a price or approving
  an item. Open state is tracked in S.openItemId and restored after list re-renders,
  including the parent category accordion being kept open.
